[ Contents ] 
🍱Tuesday / fried shirataki noodles & beef, salted rice balls
🍱Wednesday / shrimp with ketchup & mayo, tamagoyaki, sausage

🍱Saturday / chicken nanban ( sour & sweet chicken cutlet ) with pickled ginger, tartar sauce, cabbage &carrots salad

🏡Sunday breakfast /  buckwheat galette ( a thin pancake ) with egg, cheese, spinach
